#

Avocado Tuna Toast

5 min
$4.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

fishgluten (if using regular bread)

Dietary Tags:

high proteingluten-free option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

quick mealhealthyeasy

Description

A simple yet nutritious open-faced sandwich featuring creamy avocado and protein-packed tuna, perfect for a quick meal.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • canned tuna (in water): 1 can
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes: optional, to taste
